<p>The field is equivalent to all possible paths within it. Thus, to be a pocket in the field might feel exactly like every point in that field, knowing about every other point. This interaction between all points within the field gives rise to the entirety of the shape.</p>



<p>The experience of being the one electron in the topological pocket would be precisely the superposition of all possible points of view that exist within it. It aligns with what mystics have talked about for a long time – the <em><a href="https://qualiacomputing.com/2019/11/05/toy-story-4-20-movie-review/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">screen of consciousness is not fundamental</a></em>, but emergent.</p>



